  "title": "Cargo Coordinator (Fresh Graduates Welcome)",
  "description": "<p><strong><br>\n</strong>Our client is a global leader in gateway services, who is seeking to recruit a Cargo Coordinator. This position is based in Singapore.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Cargo Coordinator (Fresh Graduates Welcome)</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<p>· Handle and check cargo shipments and documentation.</p>\n<p>· Engage airlines and attend to their needs.</p>\n<p>· Liaise with third parties like agents.</p>\n<p>· Manage a team of cargo handlers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>· Nitec or diploma holders.</p>\n<p>· Preferably with relevant experience in warehousing and logistics.</p>\n<p>· Able to work on rotating shift (6 day work week, rotating shift (can be am, pm or night)</p>\n<p>· Location : East</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>JJ Consulting Services</p>\n<p>EA Licence No.: 12C6207</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Applicants are invited to send in a MS Word resume to <strong>jobs@jjconsulting.com.sg</strong> stating position applying for/present/expected salaries and earliest available date.<br>\n<br>\nWe thank all applicants in advance and regret that only short listed candidates will be notified.</p>",
